Title: Agent updater: better logging in case of a registration problem
Component: agents
State: open
Date: 2016-09-30 21:05:25
Targetversion: 1.2.8
Class: nastiness

When in the Windows agent updater there is some problem during
registrtation you can just see the error message for a couple
of milliseconds and then the window closes. Also the log file of
the updater contains *nothing*. That way it is almost impossible
to find the problem.
